  "prompt": "Where can I buy raw egg noodles/ramen in Manipal? Is there a brand?",
  "response": "In Manipal, you can find raw egg noodles or ramen at several places. Local grocery stores, supermarkets, and specialty Asian stores are good places to start looking. Some popular grocery stores in the area include:\n\n1. **More Supermarket**: Located in various places around Manipal, this supermarket often carries a variety of noodles, including raw egg noodles and ramen.\n\n2. **Big Bazaar**: Another large retail chain that frequently stocks international foods, including different brands of noodles.\n\n3. **Local Kirana Stores**: Smaller grocery stores or kirana shops may also carry raw egg noodles; it's worth checking out a few in your vicinity.\n\n4. **Online Platforms**: Websites like Amazon India, BigBasket, or Grofers may offer raw egg noodles and deliver them to Manipal. This could also be a convenient option.\n\nAs for specific brands, you might find:\n\n- **Ching's Secret**: Known for their range of noodles, including egg noodles.\n- **Maggi**: Though primarily known for instant noodles, they sometimes offer raw varieties as well.\n- **Hakka Noodles**: Various local brands produce raw egg noodles under the Hakka noodle category.\n\nRemember to check the packaging to ensure that you are purchasing raw noodles as opposed to instant or pre-cooked options. If you cannot find them locally, online shopping platforms are a great alternative.",
